    <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      A minimal, keyboard-driven note-taking application built for developers who live in the terminal.
      Fast, efficient, and distraction-free.
    </p>

    <!-- CTA Buttons -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
      <a
